ource code (298->1906 lines)\n6c48f1d Complete SDD benchmark: full project generation + validation + reports\n```\n\nThis suggests the picod JWT middleware code (auth.go, auth_test.go, server.go modifications) may have been generated as part of the SDD benchmark project generation process rather than through incremental git commits. The `changes/AR-017/` directory and all picod auth code appear to exist in the working tree but are not yet committed to git history.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n- **AgentCube** is a Go-based K8s sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents\n- **pkg/picod** is a well-structured in-sandbox daemon with 30 files covering command execution, file management (18 files in `files/` subpackage), and JWT authentication\n- **JWT middleware** is fully implemented in `auth.go` with comprehensive tests in `auth_test.go`, using RS256 with the `golang-jwt/jwt/v5` library\n- **Feature tracking** uses an AR (Architecture Request) system in `changes/AR-001/` through `changes/AR-017/`, each with proposal, design, delta-spec, and tasks documents\n- **AR-017** specifically covers the PicoD JWT Middleware feature -- the code exists but tasks are not yet marked complete, and no git commits reference it\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2875ec4d2ffeQOyIvaByjJOg68","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project","time":{"start":1775845325610,"end":1775845464158}}}}
